msgstr ""
"Фрешка в handle_cleaner_option() за шаблон за почистване с идентификатор "
"„{cleaner_id}“, XML за настройка „{option_xml}“"

#. TRANSLATORS: Warning printed to the log.
#. %s expands to the path of the XML cleaner file that was skipped
#: ../bleachbit/CleanerML.py
#, python-format
